messages.text: Hey Harry
Sup Ty! Where were you today? No one saw you in school at all.
You’ll see soon.
Aw man. Did you get into something crazy?
Yeah.
Dude. I think I already know.
Trust me. You don’t.
You and April right? Jake looked pretty pissed today.
Nah man. Nothing like that.
Well alright. So you coming over to play some x-box live?
Yeah I’ll see you soon.
Did you hear about KP? They say he ran away. His parents came to the school today and they had an assembly for people to come and say if they know where he is.
Scary isn’t it…how people keep going missing and no one knows what’s happening?
I mean it’s just been him but yeah dude it’s wild
Hey man it’s been almost 3 hours…you still coming?
I’m here.
Where dude? I don’t see you.
You’re not supposed to yet.
lol stop messing around. Come on. I got pizza.
Your dad just pulled up it’s cool. I know he doesn’t like me.
I’m out
Alright. See you in chem tomorrow
Hey I saw you in the hall today.
Really? Are you like a ninja? Cause no one has seen you again?
Yeah that’s it I’m a ninja. That’s how I know you’re eating the soup surprise for lunch right now.
Dude come sit with us. I don’t see you.
That’s cause I don’t want you to yet.
You’re acting weird bro.
the next day after school
I tried to cover for you in chem. again today. Where were you?
I passed by and just bailed. I saw you sitting next to April though. Moving in on my girl? lol
haha nah you can have her.
Actually I can’t, but what I will have is a slice of that stuff crust pizza you have in your bedroom right now.
Dude. WTH
You look scared. Don’t be. Hey you were looking a little cold after school today.
Okay this is just creepy. You stole my sweatshirt.
No this is me having a bit of fun. Besides you like using what doesn’t belong to you right? lol
Cut it out Ty!
Let’s play a game.
X-box live?
No with your mom.
Don’t go there.
She’s about to walk inside now. She should be careful. It’s a bit slippery out there.
Dude my mom just slipped. What did you do?
Do I have your attention now?
Yes!!! What is wrong with you? Why can’t you pick up when I answer. Ty is this really you?
Leave your house and make a right. But walk. And don’t tell anyone where you’re going.
No! You are really starting to tick me off man.
You can’t afford to play with me Harrison. Not today. Let’s get started.
Unless I see your face and know this is you I’m not doing anything. So back OFF!
the next morning
Good morning friend ;) you should be careful today. There are so many bad drivers out there.
Ty I’m going to kick the crap out of you when I see you.
hhmmm we will see about that…but first...
an hour later
Dude alright…alright let me go…this is your trunk I’m in the back of isn’t it?
Ssshhhh and stop it with all the kicking. You’ll mess up the interior.
Okay please bro. I’m sorry. Whatever I did just let me go. I won’t tell anyone I swear.
Calm down. Once you feel the car come to a stop the trunk will automatically open. Get out and walk 50 paces straight then turn right to see your surprise.
Why can’t I just go to school and act like everything is normal? Please. This is getting weird now.
Stop your blabbering. Be a man.
Okay I don’t see anything. Can I go now?
Open the trash can.
Dude no please. I don’t want any part of whatever this is.
You wanna listen or do you want to be next?
Oh that’s disgusting man. I think I’m going to be sick. Is that him?
Is that KP?
Yeah…or at least it was…
This is messed up. What do you want from me? What did you do to him?
It’s not what I did it’s what you did.
There’s no way you’re pinning this on me. I didn’t touch him.
You just touched the lid of the garbage can he’s in. He’s wearing your shirt. I’m no forensic scientists, but come on DNA
I have these text! You are screwed in the head. What’s wrong with you?
Tell the truth and it’ll all be over for you…you may even get your friend back.
I didn’t do this.
I haven’t told you what I want the truth about.
What???
You hooked up with April didn’t you?
Dude. That’s what this is about?
KP lied about it. I won’t keep asking you. I want the truth.
Okay yes! I did it and I was trying to play it off like it was you.
That’s unfortunate.  Only I should be with my girlfriend.
Jake? This is you isn’t it? Dude it’s not that serious. All this over some skirt?
Go 10 steps back and look in the window.
You killed Ty!!!!
And you’re next.
